  "instructions": [
    "in a large pot, combine cabbage, carrots, celery, ginger, and shallots.",
    "pour in chicken broth and bring the mixture to a boil.",
    "reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "stir in coconut milk, chinese five spice powder, salt, and black pepper.",
    "continue to simmer for another 5 minutes.",
    "stir in lemon juice and cook for an additional minute.",
    "remove from heat and let cool to room temperature.",
    "cover and refrigerate for at least 2 hours or overnight.",
    "just before serving, stir in diced cucumber.",
    "ladle the soup into bowls and serve chilled."
  ],
